Package de.fhg.iml.vlog.xfvrp.base

Interface Summary
Solution All solutions have to implement this interface with methods for accessing the report (result) or the used model with input data.
 

Class Summary
Debug Debug object is only for debugging reasons and has no influence on optimization procedures.
Node Nodes are the basic structure of this optimization model.
Quality Quality objects holds the quality of a routing solution.
TourQuality Tour qualities are used for acceleration of check process, where for each tour on the giant tour a associated tour quality holds the costs and penalties.
Util Utility class holds indifferent methods for processing on the giant tour array.
Vehicle A Vehicle encapsulates all necessary parameters like loading capacity, cost parameters or maximal route duration.
XFVRPBase<M extends XFVRPModel> XFVRPBase is the root class of all optimization methods in this framework.
XFVRPModel The XFVRPModel holds all necessary input data.
XFVRPParameter This class holds all general planning parameters, which are not allocated to certain data objects like Node or Vehicle.
 

Enum Summary
LoadType A load type describes the kind of a order.
SiteType This is the enumeration of site types.
